//Chore table test file using REST extension
### Get all chores
GET http://localhost:3000/chores

### Add a new chore
POST http://localhost:3000/chores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Take out trash",
  "description": "Take out trash before 9 PM",
  "assigned_to": "John",
  "due_date": "2025-11-05"
}

### Update a chore
PUT http://localhost:3000/chores/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Take out trash (updated)",
  "description": "Take out trash before 10 PM",
  "assigned_to": "John",
  "due_date": "2025-11-05",
  "status": "done"
}

### Delete a chore
DELETE http://localhost:3000/chores/1


